{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1702130812.816353", "card_id": "Q_633960776", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 63}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "江西税务热线回应「花 10 万买彩票中 2.2 亿」是否需缴税，称「存在争议」，如何从法律角度解读？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，江西一彩民「花 10 万买彩票中 2.2 亿」一事，持续引发网友关注。12 月 8 日下午，江西省税务局纳税服务热线工作人员回应记者称，该中奖彩民是否需要缴税，目前还存在争议，因为税法只规定到了「一次」。「至于这个‘一次’收入，是指中奖的（总）收入，还是一注的中奖收入，确实还没有相应的规定。」「花 10 万买彩中 2.2 亿」不用缴税？江西税务热线：存在争议 | 界面新闻 · 快讯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-4a21dc3da9270704ce1623f0a99638a0_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "614 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/633960776"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlonU/MWMpIwzEAMaCTEwMzE1ODY5OCC4isyrBjAAOH1AAHIJNjMzOTYwNzc2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1702130812.817360", "card_id": "Q_634052641", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 101}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中国海警「依法对菲律宾侵闯黄岩岛邻近海域的 3 艘公务船实施管控措施」，有哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "央视网消息：12 月 9 日，中国海警依法对菲律宾侵闯黄岩岛邻近海域的 3 艘渔业和水产资源局公务船实施管控措施。 中国海警依法对菲律宾侵闯黄岩岛邻近海域的公务船实施管控措施 _ 新闻频道 _ 央视网 (cctv.com)"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-28ab4bd833d0f54b782b095af3cdc2e6_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "441 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/634052641"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIlonU/MWMpIwzEAMaCTEwMzE3OTEzNSDvt8+rBjAAOKICQAFyCTYzNDA1MjY0MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1702130812.818028", "card_id": "Q_634074112", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "OpenAI 承认 GPT-4 变懒，称暂时无法修复，这意味着什么？为何会出现这一状况？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "对于越来越严重的 GPT-4 偷懒问题，OpenAI 正式回应了。 还是用的 ChatGPT 账号。我们已收到相关反馈！自 11 月 11 日以来没有更新过模型，所以这当然不是故意造成的。 模型行为可能是不可预测的，我们正在调查准备修复它。 也就是段时间内还修复不好了。 然而网友并不理解，「一遍一遍使用同一个模型，又不会改变文件」。 ChatGPT 账号澄清：并不是说模型以某种方式改变了自己，只是模型行为的差异可能很微妙，只对部分提示词有劣化，员工和客户需要很长时间才注意到并修复。 更多网友反馈，赶快修复吧，一天比一天更糟糕了。现在不但更懒，还缺乏创造力，更不愿意遵循指令，也不太能保持角色扮演了。量子位：OpenAI 承认 GPT-4 变懒：暂时无法修复"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-dc4cdf06ba666e8fa68df77c9af2bef5_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "431 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/634074112"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIlonU/MWMpIwzEAMaCTEwMzE4MzkyNCC/59CrBjAAOKEBQAJyCTYzNDA3NDExMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1702130812.819087", "card_id": "Q_602539991", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 189}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "电被发明以前，电鳗叫什么呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a70ea9c2492df47dd4dd0343f60e9edd_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "371 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/602539991"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlonU/MWMpIwzEAMaCDk2MTc4MzMyIJ6NsaMGMAA4oQJAA3IJNjAyNTM5OTkxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1702130812.819313", "card_id": "Q_633939469", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "研究称 ChatGPT 不善于辩论，而是盲目地跟从人类，这一行为意味着什么？会给人类造成什么影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "研究称 ChatGPT 不善于辩论，尽管 ChatGPT 在很多考试中成绩优秀，但人类很容易让它相信自己的答案是错的，而实际上是对的。近日，美国俄亥俄州立大学的一个研究团队与 ChatGPT 进行了各种类似辩论的对话，包括数学和一些基本常识推理，结果发现，ChatGPT 无法捍卫自己正确的信念，而是盲目地跟从人类，并且在人类的误导下不仅会放弃正确的答案，还会向人类道歉：你是对的，我为我的错误道歉。科学家称，AI 在面对相反观点时不能捍卫正确的信念，这可能会让人类处于危险中，特别是在法律和医疗健康领域。研究称 ChatGPT 不善于辩论"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-e611d2b423c2e547550f2e9c3668f36f_1440w.webp"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "219 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/633939469"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlonU/MWMpIwzEAMaCTEwMzE1Mzk0MCDy3MurBjAAODhABHIJNjMzOTM5NDY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1702130812.819844", "card_id": "Q_634011745", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 81}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何向什么都不懂的朋友说明《黑神话：悟空》的重要意义?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如题，题主的三个舍友都不玩单机，不懂 3A，题主表达能力有限，不知道如何开口。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/70/v2-4b16454517e348395a4a48c5a6f110cd_1440w.avis?source=172ae18b&biz_tag=Post"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "119 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/634011745"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlonU/MWMpIwzEAMaCTEwMzE3MDAzNyCLj82rBjAAOE9ABXIJNjM0MDExNzQ1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1702130812.820136", "card_id": "Q_398138284", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "http